headline: White Cap and DEWALT Partner to Support St. Jude Children's Research Hospital for Third Year
summary: White Cap, the leading distributor of specialty construction supplies and safety products for professional contractors, and DEWALT®, a Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE: SWK) brand and leader in total jobsite solutions, announce a third annual partnership supporting the lifesaving mission of St. Jude Children's Research Hospital®: Finding cures. Saving children®.
